<cmath>[P_1P_2P_3] = a^2 \cdot \frac{ \sqrt{3} }{4} = (2 \sqrt{3} + 2 \sqrt{7})^2 \cdot \frac{ \sqrt{3} }{4} = \sqrt{300} + \sqrt{252}</cmath>

Therefore, the answer is <math>300 + 252 = \boxed{\textbf{(D) } 552}</math>.

