Draw <math>AM</math>, <math>DP</math>, and <math>PR</math>. <math>PR</math> is parallel with <math>CD</math>

<math>[AMD] = \frac12 \cdot AD \cdot DM = 4</math>, <math>AM = \sqrt{AD^2 + DM^2} = 2 \sqrt{5}</math>

